## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of the sources accessed. Some sources may not reflect the latest research developments due to publication delays. Additionally, the complexity of psychopathology means that not all influencing factors can be comprehensively covered in a single report. Further research is recommended to explore emerging factors and their implications for mental health treatment and prevention.

